'''Kalphite workers''' are worker drones that serve the [[Kalphite Queen]]. They are found throughout the [[Kalphite Lair]] and [[Kalphite Cave]] west and east of the Shantay Pass, respectively. They cannot [[poison]], unlike the majority of [[Kalphite]]s.

Kalphite workers, like all other Kalphites, are affected by [[Keris]]. They can also be assigned to players as a [[Slayer task]]. A [[Dwarf multicannon]] can be used to fight them as they are in [[Multicombat area|multi-combat zone]].

